{"sequence":79,"timestamp":"2026-04-15T18:56:23.982594788Z","event_type":"amendment_queued","details":{"amendment_id":"fr-4-3d30bf16","body":"finding_summary: `milestone run` cannot recover a bead-backed project that was already created before `active_task_id` was recorded in the controller.\nseverity: medium\naffected_files:\n- src/cli/milestone.rs:744-766\n- src/cli/project.rs:406-417\n- src/cli/project.rs:448-499\nremediation_hint: Before falling back to `project::execute_create_from_bead`, look for an existing project whose `task_source` matches `(milestone_id, bead_id)` or at least the computed `default_project_id_for_bead`, then adopt that project into the controller instead of erroring with `DuplicateProject`.","dedup_key":"1400ca2a1b2c313168cb68bf76bc957cd6eaae48ce79beebbdedf33355d0cf10","reviewer_sources":[{"backend_family":"codex","model_id":"gpt-5.4-xhigh","reviewer_id":"reviewer-1"}],"run_id":"run-20260415164250","source":"workflow_stage","source_stage":"final_review"}}
{"sequence":80,"timestamp":"2026-04-15T18:56:23.991475498Z","event_type":"amendment_queued","details":{"amendment_id":"fr-4-de7bdf94","body":"finding_summary: Omitted-ID `milestone next` and `milestone run` abort on a stale `active-milestone` pointer instead of falling back to the active project's milestone metadata.\nseverity: low\naffected_files:\n- src/cli/milestone.rs:491-499\nremediation_hint: If `read_active_milestone` yields an ID that is malformed or no longer exists, ignore that cached pointer and then try `active_project_milestone_id` before surfacing `NoActiveMilestone` or `MilestoneNotFound`.","dedup_key":"0ddf8206ee79ba128e83253744a4c42191b62dec12009566babdeed3d5d20d58","reviewer_sources":[{"backend_family":"codex","model_id":"gpt-5.4-xhigh","reviewer_id":"reviewer-1"}],"run_id":"run-20260415164250","source":"workflow_stage","source_stage":"final_review"}}
